**Source Evidence:** `_nvms_full.txt`, `_nvms_files.txt`, `_nvms_log.txt`, `_nvms_total.txt`, `_nv_remotes.txt`, `_nv_remotes_dated.txt`, `_nvms_2025plus.txt`, `_nvms_log50.txt`, `_nvms_more.txt`
